title: Doesn't fast charge for any of our phones
body: I have a OnePlus 3 and a Realme7. It doesn't do fast charging with either of the phones or their charging bases. After 40 mins, it only charged 28%. Even my other cables that didn't do fast charging are quicker than that! So power wise, it sucks royally! But if you aren't worried about the fast charging, then it seems durable.

title: It's a dilemma.

If you want one, just buy a good quality one.  Yes it will last as it is sturdy, but it isn't durable.  I am stupid for falling for this
